adviseScripts.text: Hmm...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: The left one is the cup, and the one on the right is the bowl.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: ... Right?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Correct!
Wrong.
Yahoo!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: That was a blind guess, but I think I can see it now.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: This is the cup handle, right?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: It's not?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: But how?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: As Quiry gesticulates wildly, her hands veer dangerously close to the cup...
*Clank*
Whoops!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: We end our session while cleaning up the shards of the broken cup.
You know those documents you sent to me this morning?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: One of them is missing.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Don't forget it next time.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Are you sure that's right?
Will do. Good catch, Quiry.
I'm positive.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I may not know much about a lot of things, but documentation is one thing I excel at.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: You have no idea how hard I've trained to be good at what I do.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: No worries.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I put a lot of effort into administrative work and handling documents.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: For example, if I put my face right up against the screen, I can see it way more clearly!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I have an enjoyable time with Quiry.
*Sigh*
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I feel bad for making Poli's life so difficult.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Did you mistake her for a towel again?
Did something happen?
No, she's gotten used to that by now.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I really do feel terrible.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: It's a bit embarrassing to admit this,
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: but I mistook a radio for a snack, and...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Actually, telling someone else about it makes me feel a lot better.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I spend time consoling Quiry during our session.
How does it feel to see the world clearly?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I can't begin to imagine what it's like. Everything is always so blurry for me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: It's like looking at my face, but all the time.
It's like a haze being cleared away.
Whoa...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I totally get it!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: But I think if everything were always that clear, it'd hurt my eyes.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Hmmm...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I can't really imagine it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Even if the haze clears away, I think it'd still be kinda blurry.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Quiry and I have a conversation about seeing clearly.
*Crash*
Yikes!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Sorry, Commander, I didn't see the door...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: It's okay, I planned on swapping it out for a new one anyway.
You're not hurt, are you?
You're lying.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I'm really sorry...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Awww, you're so kind. I'm okay.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I can't say the same thing about the door though...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I'll pay for everything. Please don't tell Poli!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I spend time with Quiry mourning about the broken door.
Commander,
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: this is a super big secret,
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: but Poli recently...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: was eating something she shouldn't have been. It was brown if you catch my drift...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Actually, I enjoy eating that myself.
It's not what you think. It's just Splendamin in sweet potato flavor.
What?!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Has everyone lost their minds?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Oh!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Phew...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I need to apologize to Poli. I had the completely wrong idea...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I have a conversation with Quiry about Splendamin in sweet potato flavor.
Hmm...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: There are times where I feel my bad eyesight is actually a blessing,
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: especially since my line of work is being a police officer.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Because you can't see certain things you'd rather not see anyway?
Really?
Exactly!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: There are some things that throw even Poli and Miranda for a loop.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I feel bad when they have to cover up for my deficiencies,
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: but I still feel glad that I can't see certain things.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: ... It's a bit selfish of me, isn't it?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Yep.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: There are moments where I'd rather not see certain things.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: In those moments, I feel like I'm using my eyesight as a crutch though.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Quiry and I have a serious conversation.
Poli says that during work, I should try to stay away from Miranda as much as possible.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I know that we both get into a lot of accidents, but still...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I think we complement each other, don't you?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: No way. You'd only end up with accidents twice as big.
Definitely. You two could help each other out.
A bit harsh...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: But thank you anyway for the constructive criticism.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Poli said the same thing, probably because she was worried.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Exactly!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: But I'm sure Poli had a good reason for telling us to stay apart.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I should try to keep away from Miranda as much as possible.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I spend a meaningful time with Quiry.
Agh!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Commander! There's a bug on the desk!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I'll catch it for you.
Eeek! A bug!
*Crash*
Whoa! Did you just catch a bug with your bare hands?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Cool!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: *Gulp*
Did you... just eat it?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I see you're brave in more ways than one...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: ... I-I'll catch it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Stay still!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Oh jeez...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: *Crash*
What Quiry took for a bug, was in fact, a cookie.
This just came to me,
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: but why am I able to see you so clearly?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: This has never happened with anyone else.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Could it be because of my rank?
Because I'm special.
Hmmm...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Other commanders still look blurry to me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: There must be another reason.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Special...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: That is true...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Hehe. I'm not sure if I can see you clearly because you're special, or if you're special because I can see you clearly.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Quiry and I have a fun counseling session.
I want to be a capable police officer like Poli.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Someone who recognizes danger at a moment's notice and saves people.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: A calm, cool, and collected officer of the law who can handle any situation.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: You can do it, I'm sure of it!
... Do you really think that's possible?
You really think so?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I'll never give up!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: It's just that a lot of people will have to put up with me during the process...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I-it won't be easy but...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I don't want to give up.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Do you think I don't have it in me?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I try to encourage the dejected Quiry before ending the session.
I wish I had a hobby.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: My vision is so terrible that even that's hard.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Do you know of any new pastimes I can get into?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Swimming.
Listening to music.
Oh, good idea!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: It's not like you can see far ahead of you when you're underwater anyway.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: But I can't swim.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Oh, good idea!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: You don't need good eyesight to listen to music.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Can you recommend some songs that I should listen to?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I have a fun counseling session with Quiry.
Oh boy.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I followed someone thinking it was Miranda, but it was a stranger.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I thought for sure that I saw brown pigtails.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Is there any other way I can better pinpoint that it's Miranda?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Look carefully at how she walks.
Call out her name first.
How she walks?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Hmm, she definitely does have a distinctive bounce in her step.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Still, I don't know if that'll work.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Oh, that's a great idea!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: If it really is Miranda, she'll either respond or come closer to me.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Thanks for the tip, Commander!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I have a discussion with Quiry about how to tell Miranda apart from others.
Commander, do I have a sullen face?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: People keep asking me if I'm irritated.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I think it's because you're always frowning.
Your expression looks normal to me.
I do?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I guess it's because I'm always scrunching up my face since I can't see well.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I'll try and smile a bit more.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Thanks for letting me know, Commander!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Really?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Then how come everyone keeps telling me that I look so upset?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Is my expression that bad...?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I have a fun time advising Quiry.
Despite standing upright, Quiry keeps nodding off.
Wake her up.
Don't wake her up.
Agh...!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Sorry...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I had a ton of work to do last night, so I didn't get any sleep.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: That's no excuse for me to check out during our session, though!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: *Crash*
Ow, my head...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I have a fun time advising Quiry.
I had a lot of worries when I first came to the Outpost.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Now though, I realize this place is far more peaceful than I thought it'd be.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: In fact, it feels like there isn't much that I need to do.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: That's because the A.C.P.U. upholds the law.
So you should take a well-deserved break.
Thank you for saying that.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I was always proud to be part of the A.C.P.U., but now I'm super proud!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: No, I can't do that.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: If something were to happen while I was on vacation, I'd never forgive myself.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I have a constructive time with Quiry.
I took a day off today,
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: but I'm not exactly sure what to do with myself.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Why don't you take a nap?
Treat yourself to a nice meal.
Hmmm...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: It'd be a waste to sleep the day away.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Isn't there something else I can do?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Oooh, I like the sound of that!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: But it won't be easy with me being blind as a bat.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Are you busy, Commander?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Quiry and I plan how we'll spend her day off together.
Poli?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: What are you doing here?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Are we having a joint counseling session today?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: That's just a doll.
That's right.
Ah!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: So it wasn't Poli?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Oh right, Poli said she'd be going to the Ark on business today.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Okay!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Wait a minute...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Poli said she'd be going to the Ark on business today.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: You're not teasing me, are you, Commander?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I have a fun session with Quiry.
I'm not really sure about this, so I wanted to ask you:
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Am I a bit stronger than other people?
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: You're certainly good at breaking things.
Yes, I think so.
That...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: that is true.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: But that wasn't exactly what I meant...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I knew it!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: It feels good to find a new positive trait about yourself.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: With this strength, I'll be able to help more people.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I have a fun time advising Quiry.
Commander! I finally did it!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I'm nearly done memorizing all the roadways in the Outpost.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Now I won't get lost or break down any more doors.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Congrats!
Did you say "nearly done"?
Thank you!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I couldn't have done it without everyone's help.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Especially you, Commander. Thank you so much.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I'll keep at it and make sure I memorize every last path there is!
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: Yeah, almost...
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I've improved tremendously compared to last time, but I'm still bumping into things.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I know I've got to keep at it.
adviseScripts.speaker: Quiry

adviseScripts.text: I have a meaningful time with Quiry.
